                 agentic loop with per-turn fresh secrets and HMAC-audited
                 leak forensics.

  2026-04-27  ·  Append-only HMAC hash-chain provenance for bug-bounty
                 first-finder proofs — content-hash committed per finding,
                 each entry linking to the prior, exported as shareable
                 proof JSON without disclosing content.

  2026-04-27  ·  Tier-0 language gate (European-scripts whitelist) as a
                 pre-regex guard against transliteration bypass of
                 content-moderation patterns.

  2026-04-27  ·  Context-aware CSAM detection: codewords block always,
                 acronym allows educational/defensive (HARMFUL_VERBS vs
                 DEFENSIVE_VERBS), contextual minor+sexual always blocks.

  2026-04-27  ·  Device-level MAC-HMAC quarantine (per-install audit key,
                 no IP-ban, no central server).

  2026-04-27  ·  Immutable self-modification lock: hardcoded Python
                 forbidden-path list spanning 7 safety modules + 7 state
                 files + security docs + CI workflows.

